If an addon version has multiple xpis/jars uploaded to support multiple OSs and one has already been approved/rejected the review page still shows all files as pending review.
This can lead to a waste of time attempting to review for an OS thats already been approved.


Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Go to a review page for an addon with 2 or more supported Operating Systems
2. approve 1 file, leaving the others
3. go back to the review page
Actual Results:  
both files still show as pending review

Expected Results:  
the file you approved earlier now shows &apos;fully reviewed&apos; or &apos;preliminary reviewed&apos;, the other(s) show pending review.

the review history log shows correctly, and the admin control panel confirms approval.

Worked in Remora, doesn&apos;t in Zamboni.</thetext>
